window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Big, green, and ugly. Who says a troll can’t be the hero?</b></p> <p>Punished for his toxic online behavior, Chad faces a 30-day sentence of full-immersion therapy designed to improve his anger issues.</p> <p>For his endless trolling in real life, he's forced to play as a forest troll, the most hated race in Isle of Mythos, so that he can finally experience what it's like to be on the other side.</p> <p>To make matters worse, the heroes sent to rid the world of evil aren't heroes at all - they're violent felons on their own twisted paths to redemption.</p> <p>Playing as a monster in a world where it ain’t easy being green, what could possibly go wrong?</p> <p><b>Pick up this epic litRPG full of humor, action, and adventure today!</b></p>";